<li id="cite_note-52"><b><a href="#cite_ref-52" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://ipcc-wg1.ucar.edu/wg1/docs/WG1AR4_SPM_Approved_05Feb.pdf" class="external text" title="http://ipcc-wg1.ucar.edu/wg1/docs/WG1AR4_SPM_Approved_05Feb.pdf" rel="nofollow">IPCC Summary for Policymakers</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-53"><b><a href="#cite_ref-53" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://blogs.nature.com/climatefeedback/2007/05/the_decay_of_the_hockey_stick.html" class="external text" title="http://blogs.nature.com/climatefeedback/2007/05/the_decay_of_the_hockey_stick.html" rel="nofollow">Hans von Storch and Eduardo Zorita on the Hocky stick effect</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-54"><b><a href="#cite_ref-54" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.climateaudit.org/?p=1518" class="external text" title="http://www.climateaudit.org/?p=1518" rel="nofollow">Climate Audit - by Steve McIntyre&#160;» von Storch and Zorita blog on the Hockey Stick</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-55"><b><a href="#cite_ref-55" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://blogs.nature.com/climatefeedback/2007/05/the_decay_of_the_hockey_stick.html#comment-86863" class="external text" title="http://blogs.nature.com/climatefeedback/2007/05/the_decay_of_the_hockey_stick.html#comment-86863" rel="nofollow">Hans von Storch</a></li>
