<li id="cite_note-58"><b><a href="#cite_ref-58" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.climatescience.gov/Library/sap/sap1-1/finalreport/default.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.climatescience.gov/Library/sap/sap1-1/finalreport/default.htm" rel="nofollow">Temperature Trends in the Lower Atmosphere: Steps for Understanding and Reconciling Differences. Thomas R. Karl, Susan J. Hassol, Christopher D. Miller, and William L. Murray, editors, 2006. A Report by the Climate Change Science Program and the Subcommittee on Global Change Research, Washington, DC.</a></li>
